==========================

Date: 2026-05-14
Version: 1
Maintainer: Karl Clinger <karl.clinger@armoredgate.com>

This document lists the public-key fingerprints of all currently active
ArmoredGate signing keys. When this document is clearsigned with the
maintainer's PGP key (see TRUST-2026-05-14.txt.asc), its contents constitute
an out-of-band trust anchor that does NOT depend on ArmoredGate's own
hosting infrastructure.

To verify this document:

    gpg --keyserver keys.openpgp.org --recv-keys <KARL_PGP_FPR>
    gpg --verify TRUST-2026-05-14.txt.asc

